The localization problem is to compute the exact position and orientation of a query image.


![Image](https://github.com/users/saisriteja/projects/1/assets/48018142/1b1b5ad2-c4f4-4faa-a048-5da55da4b291)

**Application in augmented reality**
DOF localization on mobile devices - ECCV 2014
Huma POSEitioning system: SMPL models in ar space - CVPR 2021

Structure-Based Localization


![Image](https://github.com/users/saisriteja/projects/1/assets/48018142/590a4100-054c-4c75-a72c-2f2488e41ce1)

Each point in the 3d is created by matching features in 2d images.
![Image](https://github.com/users/saisriteja/projects/1/assets/48018142/b7f6aab2-f5d2-420c-be23-716094af5d71)


