Now user have edge devices and they run on the cloud to get the localization.  There are security concerns for the release of private data when uploaded.

![Image](https://github.com/users/saisriteja/projects/1/assets/48018142/70a85b53-5ba6-40b0-aa5d-292f7cdd98c6)


